{"tid":2363294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強：拘捕民主派初選人士是基於證據","createTime":"2021-01-12T05:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T07:42:13.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"43fabe6c78afa5c8dc7330ebcd72b2435cc1cc8e","tid":2363294,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:56:15.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警務處處長鄧炳強說，國安處拘捕55名組織或參與民主派初選的人士是基於證據，如果日後提出檢控，會有更多細節曝光。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強：「就此案件我們是經過調查，基於證據而作出拘捕，在這件事情發生後，我們的高級警司李桂華已就情況作出解釋，我相信這個事件日後如果去到檢控階段，大家可以看到更多細節。」<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強到啟德個案追蹤指揮中心探班，他見傳媒時又主動提到中大保安檢查站被人潑灑粉末，一名中大學生被捕的案件，說警方仍在追捕其他涉案人，批評有關行為違反中大校訓，達不到人類基本良知的要求，他作為中大畢業生，看到中大學生牽涉襲擊事件感到心痛。"},{"pid":"79df1f2e5f7ac2f9ed036e4b5c38a41cdefff8e2","tid":2363294,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:56:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=419966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D419966&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJuSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=79c1d967\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D419966&h=2cb1d4da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=419966</a>"},{"pid":"9e0ead2b6bd6fd97647bb4fae6a7d3e82d6056e8","tid":2363294,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:57:40.000Z","msg":"咩證據咁巴閉"},{"pid":"969a8f4f64a503b25f8ae86744ff226a420bc9a6","tid":2363294,"uid":334957,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:57:47.000Z","msg":"拉左大灣輝未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4ada4a56509b6ac446939c49955220d69e7f00","tid":2363294,"uid":261873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:58:33.000Z","msg":"做左國安部隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba33d6da